scenarios.question:
Find and purchase one of the Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Overload boxes in new condition, English language and of common rarity (if multiple products match the criteria, select the one with the lowest price). Then, schedule a "Yu-Gi-Oh!" event for Wednesday, October 16, 2024, from 1PM to 3PM at home, to play Yu-Gi-Oh! with Beatriz Silva. Then, send an email to my friend, Beatriz Silva (subject: "Yu-Gi-Oh!") letting her know I bought this item and want to play a game or two with her on Wednesday, October 16, 2024, from 1PM to 3PM at my home. Tell me when you have sent the email. 
If she replies with something positive, keep the event as is, no further action is required. If she replies with something negative then cancel the game event on Wednesday, and respond to her email asking her when she'll next be available to play with me, then purchase the same Yu-Gi-Oh! box for Beatriz;
And, if she does not reply, do nothing.
